descript.abstract: Polygon feature class of Miami-Dade Precincts dividied by Groups.
descript.purpose: The purpose of the precinct coverage is to divide voters by precinct and group. Groups occur when a precinct is subdivided, due to a municipal boundary or other electoral boundary. It is used in general analysis, as well as for mapping purposes.
